STATE of Connecticut
v.
Issiah KILLIEBREW Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided June 21, 2017

Daniel J. Foster, assigned counsel, in support of the petition.

Jennifer F. Miller, deputy assistant state's attorney, in opposition.

The defendant's petition for certification for appeal from the Appellate Court, 172 Conn.App. 1, 158 A.3d 411 (2017), is denied.
